<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/7629> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #7629" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/5> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cos. 128, Or[150] Cn. Octavius Cn. f. Cn. n. (20). Cos. 87. Badian (Studies 104, note 168) notes that the inscription of Delos (I. De Delos 1782; see MRR 2.26) may well refer to the future consul of 128.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/4002> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #4002" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Cic. Har. Resp. 54; Tusc. 5.55; Phil. 13.2; 14.23; Fast. Ant., Degrassi 164f., and Fast. Cap., ibid. 54f., 129f., 482f.; Ascon. 23C; App. BC 1.65-66; Dio 30-35, fr. 102.3; Eutrop. 5.4; Chr. 354; Fast. Hyd.; Chr. Pasc.; Cassiod.; on Cinna, Cic. Phil. 11.1; Vell. 2.20.3; and on Octavius, Cic. Planc. 51. Cinna was elected in Sulla's presence and swore to maintain his measures (Plut. Sull. 10.3-4; Dio 30-35, fr." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3841> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3841" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Commanded an eastern province with the title of # (I. de Delos 4.1.1782; cf. BCH 44 [1920] 303)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/3840> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #3840" ;
